{"tid":910678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【救護員】真心英雄 一碗牛腩麵 背後藏温情","createTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T02:16:16.000Z","uid":133643,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcaca999116fef1a567087d5b930cfcfcc08cbf","tid":910678,"uid":133643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"當年新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20061210/6605859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20061210%2F6605859&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMI4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=6b4a5811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20061210%2F6605859&h=76568fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20061210/6605859</a><br />\n<br />\n當前線救護人員，不時面對生離死別，當中的一點點温情，往往令悲歡離合的色彩變得温暖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fh6NVDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffh6NVDZ.jpg&h=f9e99373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入行21年的救護總隊目關家洛，在行內有「牛腩麵哥哥」的綽號，而背後，隱藏著一宗令人心酸又帶點温暖的事件。2006年，觀塘某幢唐樓的板間房內，發生一宗男童伴著母親屍體的案件，當時關Sir和上司、同事接報到場處理，結果關Sir意外地因而見報。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBAKXSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBAKXSq.jpg&h=69819b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餵伴屍童吃麵救護員獲讚賞 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCzotZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCzotZC.jpg&h=c5ef19bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關Sir回憶道：「記得走進房間，看到女士倒卧著，旁邊是一位小朋友，他很害怕。」上司在房間內為女士檢查，發現對方已離世，關Sir則陪著小男孩在外面，並嘗試和他聊天。不過孩子很害怕，很少答話，直至關Sir發現小男孩可能沒有吃飯，便到樓下的救護車拿了點餅乾，途經一家麵店時，又買了一碗牛腩麵，再回到樓上，交給小男孩。「本來想讓他自己吃，但他很害怕，在發抖，我便拿起筷子餵他，不過也只餵了幾口，我們便趕著離開了。」<br />\n<br />\n本以為事件就此告終，第二天，關Sir卻發現自己餵小男孩吃麵的照片被刊登在某張報紙的頭版，上司、母親、朋友亦輪番打電話給他追問怎麼回事。關Sir坦言當時只是憑良心做事，從未想過會引來這樣大的迴響，以至多年後，他仍然不時遇到新入職的同事稱他為「牛腩麵哥哥」，不過亦未嘗不是一件好事：「救護車出動，其實有點緊張，每天都要面對生死，但事件可以讓大家知道，當中也可以有一些温情和開心的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新生嬰兒險進馬桶<br />\n<br />\n救護人員可以用一雙手來救人、碰觸死亡，甚至迎來新生命，不過關Sir最深刻的「接生」經驗，卻有點驚險。當時關Sir和同事接報上門，快將臨盆的孕婦正坐在馬桶上，關Sir因擔心孩子會突然出生並掉進厠盆，正準備在厠盆內加墊，誰知手伸過去，小嬰兒剛好出生，被他一手接著。「孕婦的家人都很開心，再三道謝，我們亦很開心，因為好像救回了兩條生命。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源<br />\n<a href=\"http://app4.rthk.hk/special/fsd4/hero.php?aid=26\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp4.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Ffsd4%2Fhero.php%3Faid%3D26&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMI4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=6694dc82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://app4.rthk.hk/special/fsd4/hero.php?aid=26</a>"},{"pid":"369b6e9f02fb142547341479aaf29f641a170e8c","tid":910678,"uid":48241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"很感人嘅一個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5903778d783a6cafe14072284ca3b9bf9b9f7d53","tid":910678,"uid":71455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3b71e94d0087b3d1d1af556c932ff5f9d2fabf","tid":910678,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"唔知個小朋友而架點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e798e700a3f4c81aaea69795f348a54d066710d","tid":910678,"uid":48241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩火速救兵個集睇到人眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3fc718e50a97a089c96f2c15ede1e602cc160c","tid":910678,"uid":92178,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f9725b1eabb4a01f8ca99e4400c7159e969fb22","tid":910678,"uid":48241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a3fc718e50a97a089c96f2c15ede1e602cc160c","tid":910678,"uid":92178,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,